<HEAD>Eds: AMs separates on Dapporto moved as a0699, on Fairbank as a0748,
on O'Meara as a0744.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>William Fairbank</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>STANFORD, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
