<HEAD>Exxon President Says `Chance' Was Oil Spill Factor</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ROSEANNE PAGANO</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>ANCHORAGE, Alaska (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
