<FIRST>r f PM-CorporateLawyers-List     10-02 0494</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Corporate Lawyers-List,0548</SECOND>
<HEAD>With PM-Top Lawyers</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Here is a list of the 50 highest-paid corporate lawyers in <LOCATION> America </LOCATION> as estimated by <ORGANIZATION> Forbes </ORGANIZATION> magazine. Rankings include location, estimated 1988 income, law school attended and age.
